    dc:description "FIGURE 39. Diagnostic characters of Oides geiseri Lee & Beenen sp. nov. 39A.Antenna, male; 39B. Antenna, female; 39C. Penis, dorsal view; 39D. Penis, lateral view; 39E. Penis, ventral view; 39F. Apex of penis, before internal sac pulled out; 39G. Abdominal ventrite VIII; 39H. Spermatheca." ;
